  "title": "🍸 Bartender (Liveshow) | Bugis+ | Gross Up to $3,200 + Bonus + Perks",
  "description": "<h3>🕒 Working Hours:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>6 Days Work Week</li>\n  <li>Shift Timing: <strong>6:30 PM – 3:30 AM</strong></li>\n  <li>Off Days by Schedule</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>🎯 Key Responsibilities:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare and serve a wide range of alcoholic &amp; non-alcoholic beverages (cocktails, beer, sake, spirits).</li>\n  <li>Provide friendly and professional service to guests.</li>\n  <li>Manage bar operations: stock control, replenishment &amp; equipment care.</li>\n  <li>Ensure cleanliness and safety of bar, tools &amp; glassware.</li>\n  <li>Handle POS/cash transactions when required.</li>\n  <li>Support service crew during peak hours for smooth operations.</li>\n  <li>Maintain neat and tidy personal appearance at all times.</li>\n  <li>Comfortable working in a nightlife environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>✅ Requirements:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 1 year of bartending or beverage service experience preferred.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of cocktails, beer &amp; spirits (flair bartending is a plus!).</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Outgoing, positive personality with a strong work ethic.</li>\n  <li>Able to work in a fast-paced nightlife environment &amp; handle night shifts.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Perks You’ll Enjoy:</strong><br>\n✔️ Referral Bonus (bring your friends onboard!)<br>\n✔️ Medical &amp; Dental Benefits<br>\n✔️ Birthday Ang Pao<br>\n✔️ Company Transport<br>\n✔️ Incremental Annual Leave (starting from 10 days)<br>\n✔️ Career Advancement Opportunities</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Jabez Wong<br>\nEA Personnel No: R1762582<br>\nEA License No: 23C1703</p>",
